pageContext.claim: “You know, I got NATO to pay $400 billion more a year, my biggest fan in the world is Secretary General Stoltenberg of NATO. He says, I can't believe it, because we were going down every year for 20 years, it was going down, down, down, what they were paying for protection, and I came in and it looks like a rocket ship up.”
pageContext.analysis: False. NATO Secretary-General Stoltenberg made no such remark.
